name: Rocket Girls 101
description:
'''Rocket Girls 101''' ({{zh|c=火箭少女101|p=huǒ jiàn shào nǚ 101}}) was a Chinese [[Teen idol|idol]] [[girl group]] formed by Tencent through the 2018 reality show [[Produce 101 (Chinese TV series)|Produce 101 China]] on [[Tencent Video]]. The project girl group consists of eleven-members that came from different companies: [[Meng Meiqi]], [[Wu Xuanyi]], [[Yang Chaoyue]], [[Duan Aojuan]], [[Yamy]], [[Lai Meiyun]], [[Zhang Zining]], [[Sunnee]], Li Ziting, [[Fu Jing (singer)|Fu Jing]] and [[Xu Mengjie]]. They made their debut on June 23, 2018, with the single song "Rocket Girls".

As their time as a girl group was limited to only 2 years, they disbanded on June 23, 2020, and returned to their respective agencies.
